paragraphs.title: Distribution of Android and IOS over full dataset
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select inferredOS,count(inferredOS) , count(inferredOS)*100/3217857372 as twine_pct from OS where inferredOS="IOS" or inferredOS="ANDROID" group by inferredOS

%sql
select count(inferredOS) from OS where upperCC="US"

select inferredOS , count(inferredOS), count(inferredOS)*100/2380731813 as truth_pct from OS where upperCC="US" and inferredOS ="ANDROID" or inferredOS="IOS" group by inferredOS
